<item>
            <title>[LU-18823] LMR1b: Replicate MDT0000 Services to Other MDS</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18823</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Replicate and/or allow services running on MDT0000 to other MDTs/MDSes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;FID Location Database (FLDB) replication, controls FID meta-sequence mapping to MDTs and OSTs, changes very rarely&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Quota Master Target (QMT), that controls quota &lt;b&gt;limits&lt;/b&gt; which change only infrequently.  Quota &lt;b&gt;usage&lt;/b&gt; that is changing continuously can be reconstructed from the MDTs and OSTs directly in case of a failover.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;flock DLM locking, in-memory only, possibly just reconstructed like normal MDT0000 failover and lock recovery, but on another MDS&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;group DLM locking, in-memory only, possibly just reconstructed like normal MDT0000 failover and lock recovery, but on another MDS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
